Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemaj strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.33,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ťa ochránim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.86,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
