Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:30.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko tu existuje pre teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.75,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poznanie je neobmedzené.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.79,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si praješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.37,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi tvoje želanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:41.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.64,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som Shimizu Raimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal som strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:58.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Úprimne, mala som 100 krát večší strach ako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Diki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.54,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže takto to bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:08.37,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď Miharu je nezodpovedný a pokojný, vôbec nieje bezcitný.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.86,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V poriadku! Tak poďme!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:12.72,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak kam?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:14.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do Fumskej dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.70,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(596,650)}www.slovak-anime.tym.sk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:25.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuumský ninjovia sa striedajú v čarovaní hmlového umenia, aby skryli dedinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:31.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemala by byť skrytá hmlovým umením?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:34.48,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo sa blíži.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:42.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Títo ľudia sú ninjovia z dediny Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.32,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydržte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.37,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som tiež Fuumský ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:38.72,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:42.01,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai-Kairoushuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:42.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo ich päť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.61,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snažila som sa ich zastaviť...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:50.11,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale oni sa dostali do dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:54.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeden z nich je monštrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:54.74,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Monštrum!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On zrušil hmlové umenie... každému...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.59,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor, ošetrím ti tvoje zranenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.39,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba jej telo bolo zranené...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.59,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...ale oblečenie nieje poškodené.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Može to byť...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to je nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:23.52,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinjutsu, Zakázaná technika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:23.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím ochrante Fuumský zvitok kinjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prosim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:52.42,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach jaj. Mohol by si nám proste dáť úprimnú odpoveď.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.57,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kairoushuu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz, mi prosím odpovedz na moju otázku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, čo si myslíš že robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.94,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je mŕtvy, ako nám odpovie na tu otázku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:18.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tajné dvere? To je starý trik
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže tade utiekli?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená, že {\i1}to{\i0} vzali so sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.16,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potrebujeme sa spojiť s Kotarou-dono, čo najskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.68,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je zvitok kinjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je hneď za domom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba jeden? S tím si poradíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to vravel že je hneď za domom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne nieje dôvod sa na to pítať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:02.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah jaj, je úplne neschopný, ale hlavná vec že má plné ústa kecov.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.84,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Našiel som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.28,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.63,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je vporiatku nechať Shinrabanshou tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:53.46,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím tomu. Zdá sa že ešte nieje v stave, aby to aktivoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatial ho môžeme nechať tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz musíme dokončiť iné veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.93,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš Fuumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.08,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounin, najvyšší ninja rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.06,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Už som poslal päť jouninov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to stačiť, keď ich je len päť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.16,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, typ tajného umenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.16,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uživateľ Kira je medzi nimi, nieje dôvod sa obávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.24,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...ak je ten chlapec medzi nimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.49,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sme uprostred nastavovani komunikačných kanálov s úradmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:23.99,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je čas, aby sme zahájili náš plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:29.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A k tomu potrebujeme Fuumský kinjutsu zvitok, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.03,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevraveli sme vám hneď na začatku....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...že nikoho nezabijeme ak nám to vydáte?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:49.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Každý z vás je tak tvrdohlavý ako tý ninjovia, ktorý slúžili generálom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Používanie zbraní je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je neobvyklé, aby ninja používal pištoľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.26,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme sa stále spoliehať na ninja techniky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.28,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nielen že ste tvrdohlavý, ale tiež stále žijete v minulosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvaj, 21. storočie je éra jedinečností.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.62,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To musí byť ono, to je Fuumský kinjutsu zvitok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.01,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca, Yukimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Náš šéf bude potešený našou prácou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:21.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajímalo by ma... i keď sme získali toto, tak by to mohlo byť nanič.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:26.91,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak, potrebujeme to kinjutsu k získaniu Shinrabanshou, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:27.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:33.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je základným pravidlom ninjou, aby sa stiahli ako náhle skončia úlohu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoite, vrácame sa späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy bastardi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak, že tu ešte niekto zostal....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dajte si pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Týto chlapci sú silný.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich úroveň je sa líši od Yamaseho a ostatných, niektorý nás napadli v Bantene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.31,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Štyria ľudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.07,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne len traja ľudia, niesu vôbec zlý.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach jaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:43.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoite, postaraj sa o neho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:41.37,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaj jaj, nemusel tak dopadnúť, keby nám to vydal bez tých cavykov.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:43.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.11,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinrabanshou je tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:48.91,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To dieťa s tým tupým pohľadom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nečakal som že by sme tu na neho mohli naraziť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.04,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To by mohol byť problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo máme urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.28,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu, čo sa stalo s Fuuma-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.96,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne nieje v dedine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby tu bol, tak by sa toto nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.01,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To nieje dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:18.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo môže teraz Kotarou robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.63,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Kinjutsu je dušou tejto dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Za každú cenu ju získam späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:26.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, rozumiem ti ako sa cítiš, ale musíš sa upokojiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mala by si byť schopná odhadnúť, ako sú silný.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kairoushuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.43,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...má eso v rukáve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.49,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je druhé ninja umenie: Vyhrať útekom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.28,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai sa nikdy neotočí k nepriateľovi chrbtom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.73,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Momentálne sme nemali do dediny vôbec chodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.99,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten ninja s klobúkom je asii...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...monštrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.04,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpečatenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Shimizu, dajte pozor na Rokujoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.72,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, a čo vy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.34,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ich zdržím...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.78,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...chodte bez mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.57,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi, tade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu, priprav sa na beh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím odviesť ich pozornosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Raimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.41,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitaj doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:01.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Za nimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.58,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nečakala som, že tak skoro narazím na Kairoshouu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.59,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bežte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:25.94,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to je úžasné dievčatko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Na ninju sa vieš pekne oháňať mečom, hraješ sa na samuraja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Neharajem sa, ja som samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:38.07,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Samuraj, huh? Teraz keď o tom premýšľam, tak máme tiež niekoho takého.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.33,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.62,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je ten človek!? Odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.08,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože, dievčatko? Ty ho poznáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Neutekaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:01.26,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chystám sa od neho získať odpovede.Kde ten človek je a čo práve robí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzeral veľmi ťažkopádne, ale pohyboval sa ako opica
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj ho na mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.42,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa budeš chovať frajersky, tak dostaneš na držku, hajzeľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje kecenie je poľutovaniahodné..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:39.14,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka svojim slabým trikom len vyzeráš čoraz viacej ako dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.48,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď som ťa predtým varoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.82,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poľavil si pozornosť, pretože som dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.49,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidím že sa ti darilo, súdiac podľa tvojej tváre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.74,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninjovia bojujú medzi sebou na doraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokiaľ ste milý k nepriateľovi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...nemali by ste byť vo svete Nabari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:19.68,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď získať Hijutsu nie je časťou misie, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:23.55,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dávať niečo navyše do toho, čo nie je v pláne, je proti mojim zásadám.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:28.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No,nazvime túto potýčku nešťastnou náhodou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.21,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj! Ako sa voláš!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.48,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebal by si ho zastavovať..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobá voľba, okuliarnik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.78,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poviem ti ho, až sa znova stretneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:47.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoite, neponáhľame sa získať Shinrabanshou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni si a vráť sa..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumohira-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:02.06,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte stále by tu mohli byť Kairoushuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.29,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdržiavať sa tu je dosť nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:03.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechajme ho na Thobari-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:11.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je našou povinnosťou ťa bezpečne niekam dostať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raimei-san má pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.41,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je o tom pochýb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.46,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumohira-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:37.42,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drž sa vzadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On používa kinjutsu, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.36,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinjutsu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.26,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu, ty debil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:59.48,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teoreticky by ro mali byť podobné Cínskému Qigon, ktoré využíva chi, ktorée preteká všetkými vecami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.39,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Udrieme svojho protivníka svojim chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...a zvnutra mu poškodíme jeho telo a krvný obeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi ktorým zautočíme, je časťou vlastnej vitality...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Použivanim jeho vlastnej životnej sily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.78,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostal som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Od-Odpečatiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpečať to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:14.93,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je rýchly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rokujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.12,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty krvácaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.46,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinrabanshou-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vadí mi to keď sa pozeráš inde...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:22.24,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje umenie ma ešte uplne neudrelo, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumohira-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdrhaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.07,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...iba po mne, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusť môjho učitela.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.01,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty debil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto s týmto nemá nič spoločné.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.21,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...čo  teda vlastne chceš?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.44,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokiaľ idete po mne, pôjdem s vami do Igy alebo kamkoľvek budete chcieť..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezahrávaj sa so mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:20:00.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď to bude stáť veľa obetí, nikomu nedáme Hijutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.83,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:08.96,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lenže, pokiaľ je to tak,tak by sme tu boli celkom zbytočne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď hovoríš, že to s nami nemá nič spoločného...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš povedať, že nemáš nič s nami spoločné?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to lepšie, že nemáš nič s nami spoločné?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:25.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:31.19,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubil som ti, že ťa nenechám umrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak si pohni a zmizni odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A snaž sa za každú cenu stretnúť s Fuuma-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď! Rokujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:52.88,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:12.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.57,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach jaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:35.46,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy by som sa nenazdal, že niekto dokáže zlomť mis technique tak rýchlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj tak je to veľký prúser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:59.56,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravil si  i na dvore pekný bordel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:44.26,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've removed Shinrabanshou from my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:46.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...nechel by si si to nechať?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:50.81,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem sa do toho zaplietať.
